<subSubSection pageId="268" pageNumber="873" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="268.[1378,2586,253,758]" pageId="268" pageNumber="873">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1381,1727,523,557]" pageId="268" pageNumber="873">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Habitat loss may be a majorrisk to the Edented Sulawesi Rat. It occurs in Pegunungan Latimojong Hutan Lindung Protected Forest. There are few details regarding it natural history, so more research is needed.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
